       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CBL0003.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-COUNTER     PIC 9(2) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-TOTAL       PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           PERFORM ACCUMULATE
               VARYING WS-COUNTER FROM 1 BY 1
               UNTIL WS-COUNTER > 10.
           DISPLAY "SUM 1-10: " WS-TOTAL.
           STOP RUN.
       ACCUMULATE.
           ADD WS-COUNTER TO WS-TOTAL.
